---
description: Cursor Rules for TypeScript / TSX files
globs:
  - "*.ts"
  - "*.tsx"
alwaysApply: true
---

rules:

- id: run-quality-checks-on-every-change
  description: Always run format, lint, and typecheck whenever Cursor writes/changes files
  triggers:
  - after_write
    actions:
  - run: pnpm run format:fix
  - run: pnpm run lint:fix
  - run: pnpm run typecheck

- id: prefer-clean-code
  description: Encourage clean, typed, readable output
  message: |
  Always generate code that:
  - passes ESLint
  - is formatted by Prettier
  - has correct TypeScript types
